titles.title: For the relief of Ulrike Sanders.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Judiciary.

bill.summary: 2/9/1994--Introduced. Directs the Attorney General to parole into the United States a named individual under the same conditions as the Attorney General prescribed for her parole in August 1992.
